Revision history of pluma

1.3
* Tue Aug 12 2008 Scott Schneider <sschneid@gmail.com>
- Added ability to change user's cn, gidNumber, homeDirectory, mail, and uidNumber
- Fixed bug of loginShell being pushed to LDAP whether modified or not
- Fixed bug of search results returning a single user with no cn would result in an internal server error
- Fixed bug complaining about non-existing match element in [displayUser] group membership

1.2
* Wed Jul 30 2008 Scott Schneider <sschneid@gmail.com>
- Added password-changing method
- UI tweaks (removed color-themed dividers, smaller CSS footprint)

1.1
* Mon July 28 2008 Scott Schneider <sschneid@gmail.com>
- initial changelog created
